# Production / preview builds: set these in Cloudflare Pages → your project → Settings →
# Environment variables → **Build** (not in GitHub). Static export inlines NEXT_PUBLIC_*
# at compile time. For local dev, copy to `.env` or set in your shell.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTACT_EMAIL=you@example.com

# Optional: force asset base path (default on Cloudflare/GitLab/etc. is root "").
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=
